239
00:10:58,227 --> 00:10:59,717
for this season's acceptable lengths.

240
00:11:00,368 --> 00:11:02,395
Which means I either have to alter or shop.

241
00:11:02,564 --> 00:11:03,522
To be or not to be.

242
00:11:03,733 --> 00:11:05,631
Just wait 'til you hear what InStyle thinks of you, young lady.

243
00:11:05,892 --> 00:11:07,014
What time are you getting home tonight?

244
00:11:07,210 --> 00:11:09,717
We have to go over the special graduation edition of the Franklin,

245
00:11:09,819 --> 00:11:11,836
and of course we're completely behind, partly because Paris

246
00:11:11,883 --> 00:11:14,833
can't let anything go to print unless she's proofed it a million times.

247
00:11:14,929 --> 00:11:18,212
- Can you say crazy anal micromanager?
- Not five times fast.

248
00:11:18,319 --> 00:11:20,060
- I'll be home by ten.
